Feature	                      Hashtable	                   ConcurrentHashMap

Thread Safety	              Yes (whole table locked)	   Yes (bucket/segment locked)
Performance	                  Slower (high contention)	   Faster (low contention)
Null Keys/Values	          Not allowed	               Not allowed
Introduced	                  Legacy (pre-Java 2)	       Modern (Java 5+)
Usage	                      Rarely used	                Preferred for concurrency